OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780924279
OL,3,CRare red-ruffed lemur quadruplets born
OL,4,Cat small conservation zoo
OL,6,FCritically endangered red-ruffed lemur
OL,7,Fquadruplets have been born at a small
OL,8,Fwildlife charity's zoo in Devon.
OL,10,FShaldon Wildlife Trust, says while
OL,11,Ftwins are common for the species,
OL,12,Fquadruplets account for fewer than six
OL,13,Fper-cent of births worldwide.
OL,15,FRed-ruffed lemurs are only found in a
OL,16,Fsmall area in the Northeast of
OL,17,FMadagascar.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
