PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780924279
OL,3,CRare red-ruffed lemur quadruplets born
OL,4,Cat small conservation zoo
OL,6,FThe quadruplets arrived at the zoo in
OL,7,FShaldon, Teignmouth on Monday 4 May to
OL,8,Fmother Eka and father Nero. Shaldon
OL,9,FWildlife Trust says the birth of four
OL,10,Fhealthy infants at once is testament
OL,11,Fto the care its team provides.
OL,13,FDirector Zak Showell said: "The four
OL,14,Fyoungsters are already keeping mom,
OL,15,FEka, very busy. Visitors to the Trust
OL,16,Fmay soon be able to catch a glimpse of
OL,17,Fthe youngsters as they become more
OL,18,Factive in their habitat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780924279
OL,3,CRare red-ruffed lemur quadruplets born
OL,4,Cat small conservation zoo
OL,6,F"There is nothing quite like the
OL,7,Farrival of 'quads' to remind us why we
OL,8,Fdo what we do."
OL,10,FThe newborns are part of the European
OL,11,FAssociation of Zoos and Aquariums
OL,12,F(EAZA) breeding programme, a Europe-
OL,13,Fwide effort to ensure the survival of
OL,14,Fred-ruffed lemurs.
OL,16,FShaldon Wildlife Trust also directly
OL,17,Fsupports the protection of these
OL,18,Fanimals in the wild through its field
OL,19,Fconservation partner, the Lemur
OL,20,FConservation Association (AEECL).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
